<section class="section" data-section-id="{{ section.id }}">
  <h2 class="section-title">FAQ</h2>
  <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What can I do with the samples? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Samples are for color and texture review only. They help you compare colors in your actual outdoor light before planning a bulk material order.</div></div>
  <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How long does shipping take? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Sample kits ship to the U.S. in 7–12 business days. You will receive a tracking number once your order is dispatched.</div></div>
  <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Can I order bulk materials after receiving samples? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Yes! After reviewing your samples, submit a Project Estimate with your photos, area, and timeline. We'll prepare a custom bulk material quote.</div></div>
  <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Are the samples refundable? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">If your kit arrives damaged, contact us within 48 hours with photos for a replacement.</div></div>
</section>

